\begin<<3216>>tex2html_deferred<<3216>>\par\end<<3217>>tex2html_deferred<<3217>>
\begin<<1928>>theorem_type<<1928>>[algorithm][theorem][][][][]
強度を用いた直接<tex2html_comment_mark>1173
